---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Terramation UK"
  description="How Terramation UK handles newsletter sign-ups, contact form enquiries, and basic website analytics."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb__sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <span aria-current="page">Privacy Policy</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page-header__sub">
        We only collect the information needed to reply to enquiries and send campaign updates you have asked for.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="prose">
        <p>
          Terramation UK respects your privacy. This page explains what personal data we collect, why we collect it,
          and how you can contact us about it.
        </p>

        <h2>What we collect</h2>
        <p>
          When you use our newsletter form, we collect your email address and any name details you choose to provide.
          When you use our contact form, we collect the details you submit so we can respond to your enquiry.
        </p>

        <h2>How we use it</h2>
        <p>
          We use newsletter data to send updates about human composting, terramation, and the Close the Circle campaign.
          We use contact form data to reply to questions, campaign enquiries, and advertising requests.
        </p>

        <h2>Who processes the data</h2>
        <p>
          Newsletter sign-ups are processed through Brevo for email delivery and double opt-in confirmation.
          Contact form submissions are processed through our website and delivered to the site owner using Brevo's
          email infrastructure.
        </p>

        <h2>Your choices</h2>
        <p>
          You can unsubscribe from campaign emails at any time using the link in any email we send. If you want us to
          update or delete information you have shared through this website, email
          <a href="mailto:info@terramation.uk"> info@terramation.uk</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy questions, contact <a href="mailto:info@terramation.uk">info@terramation.uk</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
